To use the tablet as an input device we use:

$  git clone https://github.com/rfc2822/GfxTablet


Install GfxTablet apk from F-droid (look for the apk in google) or by compiling it from github.


You need the IP of the computer for the apk, use:

$  ifconfig | grep inet | head -1 | awk '{print $2}'


To record a word and get a .xy file:

$  bash getWord.bash
